des: The Diocese of Bridgeport’s Institute for Catholic Formation invites you to test your knowledge of the Catholic faith. Great for the classroom or the family room. Play The Catholic Quiz by saying "Alexa, Launch Test My Catholic Faith", listen to the question, and respond with the correct answer (A, B, C, or D).
